          "Finish by descending into Kunming Old Street for Yikeyin courtyard remnants and narrow heritage alleys, then continue to Nanqiang Street and Jinma Biji if dusk has arrived. This final stretch works best in the evening, when the arcades light up, food stalls get busy, and the archways mark the centre of town. Return to Old Street for dinner."
